Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:38.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\Fade(100,100)}靈魂歸於靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:50.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\Fade(100,100)}我將不再復述
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:58.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\Fade(100,100)}請記住此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:14.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\Fade(100,100)}帶著你的心到
