Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:48.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,こわして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.42,0:22:51.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,私の心を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:58.65,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,赤い悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:06.03,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,あふれて流れてくるから
