Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.12,0:23:37.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,今はただ　ah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:40.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ひとみ閉じ　ah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.99,0:23:46.22,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,砕けてしまいたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.87,0:23:55.98,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そばにいてね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:34.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能擁抱
